title: Gateway Worship - Gateway Next - Look Up
description:
Look Up is the the first project from gatewayNEXT, the worship team from Gateway's Amazing Kids ministry. This project was created to minister to the next generation. 

Look Up is filled with songs and words of declaration inspiring young hearts to be bold in their response to the voice of God that speaks openly with them. This first album will capture the attention of the next generation that is already changing their present world with their boldness, while building up their faith to be the catalyst for change tomorrow. 

These original songs have been written and recorded with the same heart that comes from the leadership of Gateway Worship, and their powerful expression of worship. gatewayNEXT is a natural extension of the passionate pursuit of God already established at Gateway, and Look Up serves as a glance into their journey of discovery and understanding of the power and presence of god in their daily lives.
